{"tid":2498993,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚lihkg商用車學神 (10)","createTime":"2021-04-21T14:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T17:16:25.000Z","uid":119708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"681931c4c4808c581dc97030eba5bbc09b373a5f","tid":2498993,"uid":119708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"上個 post：<br />\n召喚lihkg商用車學神 (9)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2473088/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2473088/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">商用車討論區</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n商用車：<br />\n4（私家小巴）<br />\n5（公共小巴）<br />\n6（的士）<br />\n9（私家巴士）<br />\n10（公共巴士）<br />\n17（專利公共巴士）<br />\n18（中型貨車）<br />\n19（重型貨車）<br />\n20（掛接車輛）<br />\n<br />\nFAQ：<br />\nQ1)唔同學院用咩車考，有咩優劣？<br />\n<br />\n巴士<br />\n普遍嘅駕駛學校都係用棍波黎教e.g.德安、有記個d。車型方面普遍係宇通，特點係難入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS5yz8xXL37vmfbUZo6QtVyLMQk9JJwiY8s6FzjK8S8n1?filename=GaBmnUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaBmnUL.jpg&h=6c6eff3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於自動波巴士，只有李健、鏗鏘同有記有。李健用benz鏗鏘用man有記用宇通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbenz代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYM8upY4WnH2tXWefuLXrdFkbNDPAaNPeitnYCXvp9Koa?filename=L7hgWeR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7hgWeR.jpg&h=49760d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nman代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdxGXVBcdPLynUVC6Y9jFDYF4qhSxzcshZc1VxHGCbPiJ?filename=wVGBbOe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVGBbOe.jpg&h=f59e0de4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n宇通代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcLaUz4C82x8YCyJRLrF1Kp6h5LmrpWoqU8P9cmSnNDHy?filename=7Qo9asT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Qo9asT.jpg&h=603f5fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n   <br />\n講起自動波巴士，點少得巴士公司嘅巴士，只係一般人唔會用佢黎學<br />\n九巴代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb4f7Q4fXYx4qGDdteCVJ7t9ZSVLWdzGCLsn7eR3rr3n6?filename=KuhD9z8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuhD9z8.jpg&h=13686fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPcxsUHhpqdG1afkeBiqQKApWM7B77jgUh1pJ13p2LLgw?filename=KEzWbOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEzWbOv.jpg&h=da637bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新巴代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQKdLT5zZmSe6csagDUGDFfb5jWTjkc6vLMf4Lm2bR49N?filename=KypyYtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKypyYtA.jpg&h=ca021e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中型貨車<br />\n現時各駕駛學校都係用9噸車黎教，以車身黎講有d 5.5輕型貨車都大過佢，而且係用風迫力風手制，用油壓迫力個d假9中型好似得返2部。常見車型有isuzu NQR 9.0同JAC 9噸。據聞JAC個避震可以話冇，所以舒適度應該會差過isuzu好多。<br />\n<br />\nisuzu NQR 9.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfZx7W62kLGxFG8P2KxNVa3khhXbs7SNTgygnneSC3LgM?filename=3spGnVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3spGnVs.png&h=cf2ada37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網話呢款車係用普通手制，但呢款學神車為咗符合運輸署要求已經改咗用風手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJAC 9噸  <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQE1Ehuyv1d5oC9MqU5uszMBh1U43aDXbwuQYjbbL3x6v?filename=9wdoBfy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wdoBfy.jpg&h=79e8e571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeKaDLgnBoBkmSE15XvA3AQC1r971NQ9fp72Q7k1xVN5t?filename=aXckDtU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXckDtU.jpg&h=1c0459be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小巴<br />\n宜家學神小巴清一色係粉藍色真小巴，車型就普遍係街上見到嘅toyota coaster。李X就用三菱rosaz。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豐田Coaster<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUAQqaUgAEVKZ2AEYqPt7SoaMHXfmdrbBrc8SXxLVtFpz?filename=zjRugqu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjRugqu.png&h=4bb10429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三菱Rosa<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTewRv4yNrdEfNn974jFniuidC5BTxP5vBTptU9wjSQrD?filename=nfXQLiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfXQLiX.jpg&h=cd2c7d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實小巴個size同巴士個size差唔多，而且個試場已經搬咗去德士古道，學得小巴不如直接學巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重型貨車<br />\n基本上所有駕駛學校都係用30噸嘅車黎考。車型方面清一色用日本車，分別係hino 700、isuzu CYH同UD (型號不詳)，全港只有3部hino同1部UD，其餘都係isuzu。李健有2部hino同2部isuzu，鏗鏘就3部isuzu，好運就1部hino。<br />\n<br />\nIsuzu CYH<br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmStWbF5o6zU9moiuMauAUgAKGV89KN5WpofKPbQmdNDZX?filename=myMNit0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyMNit0.png&h=01e75f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHino 700<br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZn6YYjd7R8xS6ft9cKMP5aSvUYSExQsdf6BND54Sfvaw?filename=yBT72VK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBT72VK.png&h=965e5f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貨櫃<br />\n貨櫃嘅車款同重型差唔多普遍都係以isuzu呢個牌子為主。除咗日系牌子之外仲有man同scania呢2個歐洲牌子嘅稀有品種，但就只有鏗鏘同駕院有得揸。學貨櫃你可以揀20尺架或40尺加學，各有優勝之處但駕院只有20尺架學。<br />\n<br />\nIsuzu代表<br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYkWL7J9o67VLUWndpFzTjANfrFiNMiVvEQWFXvNmeCm?filename=SpJTd2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpJTd2t.jpg&h=56c20419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHino代表<br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVoYVU4KC9kU7su9aALRBnKUuSkzYwZiaD3QB3iPNd2Yx?filename=1KUZT2y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KUZT2y.jpg&h=04cdd373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMan代表<br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVVm8DhLva6dzRK1pDQsk7fHZkVQiqy8YUjJZd51LxnoP?filename=a1XQgfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1XQgfX.png&h=fad8c771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQdu2MFo1LhtkBU8THrem7tvqRmKxsqHForAQne9Ktu3A?filename=70yzHVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70yzHVY.jpg&h=fffe91d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nScania代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNbeJMWK8NcuQJaK62mftgBQQcef56UzeRavWUNMpH6dx?filename=qVBET2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVBET2F.jpg&h=af3c9789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部分圖片只係網上搵返黎，有機會會up下d真相上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ2)黎緊10月1號轉制，有咩條件可以考商用車？<br />\n<br />\n考牌資格:<br />\n10月1號後，只需完咗P牌就可以考商用車，唔洗再等多2年，但其他限制就不變。(e.g.須21歲以上)<br />\n<br />\n拎牌資格:<br />\n10月1號後，據運輸署網頁顯示，拎的士、小巴、巴士牌之前需要上合共16 (8+8)小時職前訓練課程同完成考核，否則冇得拎牌。簡單d黎講姐係要考2次筆試(基礎單元及專屬單元)後先有得拎牌。<br />\n每份卷有25題MC，答啱多過15題就為止合格，限時30分鐘<br />\n「基礎單元」三個牌通用，所以只需要讀一次，但「專屬單元」就每個牌都要讀一次，例如考晒的士牌、巴士牌同小巴牌，就要上8+8+8+8小時<br />\n<br />\n10月1號後拎商用車車牌流程:<br />\n中型貨車&amp;重型貨車(要先有1/2牌):<br />\n報名-&gt;學車-&gt;考車-&gt;拎牌<br />\n<br />\n貨櫃車(要先有18/19牌):<br />\n報名-&gt;學車-&gt;考車-&gt;拎牌<br />\n<br />\n小巴&amp;巴士(要先有1/2牌):<br />\n報名-&gt;學車-&gt;考車-&gt;(上堂-&gt;筆試) x2 -&gt;拎牌<br />\n<br />\n的士(要先有1/2牌):<br />\n報名-&gt;筆試-&gt; (上堂-&gt;筆試) x2 -&gt;拎牌<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">**宜家已經過咗10月1日，呢日打後入紙申請考牌嘅請各位乖乖咁上堂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce7fe1e280ae97a7d7a2407cad44b358a375e20","tid":2498993,"uid":119708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"Q3)宜家報名考試要等幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n可以上運吉個網睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://eapps2.td.gov.hk/repoes/td-es-app517/WaitingTimeExtPreview.do?language=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feapps2.td.gov.hk%2Frepoes%2Ftd-es-app517%2FWaitingTimeExtPreview.do%3Flanguage%3Dzh&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=5a429c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eapps2.td.gov.hk/repoes/td-es-app517/WaitingTimeExtPreview.do?language=zh</a><br />\n<br />\nQ4)考試及格之後點樣拎個牌？<br />\n<br />\n其實同當初考私家車/輕型貨車之後拎 P 牌一樣，填表、準備文件，七個工作日後（的士可以即時）上運輸署申請（詳情請睇 TD 557）<br />\n不過你本身已經有張正式駕駛執照，所以只需要加簽，有效期不變，無需再畀 $548"},{"pid":"c07e17a8f48e629d259c6eaa2c4fd5764c22a7ae","tid":2498993,"uid":119708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"考牌路線：<br />\n<br />\n柴灣中型 (A)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSxjVSZrXQpfcThcgUV7pFDi6iSCtisRpqUNWxKG9A3gL?filename=QdWEmRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdWEmRy.png&h=78334c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柴灣中型 (B)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmabmRhbw12kkbXLnDsE6eWk3myQyDVwTA1hEQjfWGDEUa?filename=m9UZmRz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9UZmRz.png&h=e80c67a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n柴灣中型 (C)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY9qSthh1c6nHFACeAZ6PwzquBqU6FfGpk7FtnZDzG2Lk?filename=3Fgg8wA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Fgg8wA.png&h=cd083b40&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n荃灣中型 (大窩口)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSviVfYw2jb9Wqvz6DZPtK5oSuB8r6TzeC7QB3V1weZ1V?filename=pB9RGyq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB9RGyq.png&h=f653bb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣中型 (永建路)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWR8qCeTQqacZxXzzTVcP3D58KyiJ1i7edgBEDk5oH3Fh?filename=vzVUEj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzVUEj6.png&h=92f64d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣中型 (永基路)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaQc8nbfdyM6Z7PFsescd6dJf1nm1Wk8tgub1Ek4VmiWd?filename=bBWAoMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBWAoMM.png&h=7acdca9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣巴士 (A) 柴灣巴士調頭唔洗入盛泰里，只係google map唔俾我set中途調頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfVhaNu3hrDEXj2N16saiAV9et6TQxxPkHMX8PAHHe5X4?filename=W17oOwB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW17oOwB.png&h=835c63e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n柴灣巴士 (B) 柴灣巴士調頭唔洗入盛泰里，只係google map唔俾我set中途調頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaLxUznuMM3BVTuVpkR4V6GFiPDr26npDbCQSCrrY6v4A?filename=xJNoOwB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJNoOwB.png&h=fc72d789&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n荃灣巴士 (大窩口) <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaPjw3V2KkQrup3aMP9r3wMXkTUSyJs3RMr7G9WnQCgRR?filename=EscDmCm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEscDmCm.png&h=5bb2e4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣巴士 (葵盛圍)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUzCdBP18VNY8s4qDmugPf3nFmCkZ4KDWCfbtUtVZwmcB?filename=0fVtJMO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fVtJMO.png&h=e6a68014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣重型 (沙咀道上大窩口)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdRGNrZopoxEt7A878Y24WbZ9gg3A1adkSaMyZ19c9Yd2?filename=DXnvW7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXnvW7r.png&h=0ba6a151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣重型 (楊屋道上大窩口)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc4RoivfUeGemJ9ny78s3CPxYW1n1aDbfcCq4Tsy5GsJA?filename=GttSq0M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGttSq0M.png&h=35280f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣重型 (葵盛圍)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSWZzxV3gFW4RKo65kpHnZSZS81eieg4CqGyJraruEZ7e?filename=QGYK1y7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGYK1y7.png&h=525b3904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br /